ition: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"states 01\"\n        title=\"states 01\"\n        src=\"/u-design/static/4b016241fbc8cb9dceb791df43bd8fba/07a9c/states_01.png\"\n        srcset=\"/u-design/static/4b016241fbc8cb9dceb791df43bd8fba/f21e7/states_01.png 360w,\n/u-design/static/4b016241fbc8cb9dceb791df43bd8fba/37523/states_01.png 720w,\n/u-design/static/4b016241fbc8cb9dceb791df43bd8fba/07a9c/states_01.png 1440w,\n/u-design/static/4b016241fbc8cb9dceb791df43bd8fba/e8950/states_01.png 2000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"设计说明\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E\" aria-label=\"设计说明 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>设计说明</h2>\n<h3 id=\"避免使用占位符作为标题\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E9%81%BF%E5%85%8D%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%8D%A0%E4%BD%8D%E7%AC%A6%E4%BD%9C%E4%B8%BA%E6%A0%87%E9%A2%98\" aria-label=\"避免使用占位符作为标题 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>避免使用占位符作为标题</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>避免使用占位符作为标题，因为一旦填写表单，占位符文本就会被覆盖；当占位符不再可见时，必须使用标签来指示表单字段的含义。</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1440px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 15%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAADCAYAAACTWi8uAAAACXBIWXMAAAsTAAALEwEAmpwYAAAAW0lEQVQI143MSwqAMAwE0N7/omo/SdOPcTdiqwVFxMWQMAzPpKS4IrK2y1zhnIz/6HPW1hGV2/YZ8wrGihASOCo8KYi3lsUW+FDHVuQvyCfIHePYwWlOsK58gjs4mOYUhPv9GQAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"descriptions 01\"\n        title=\"descriptions 01\"\n        src=\"/u-design/static/08e0ece05a16ebfce318b275bce47e27/07a9c/descriptions_01.png\"\n        srcset=\"/u-design/static/08e0ece05a16ebfce318b275bce47e27/f21e7/descriptions_01.png 360w,\n/u-design/static/08e0ece05a16ebfce318b275bce47e27/37523/descriptions_01.png 720w,\n/u-design/static/08e0ece05a16ebfce318b275bce47e27/07a9c/descriptions_01.png 1440w,\n/u-design/static/08e0ece05a16ebfce318b275bce47e27/e8950/descriptions_01.png 2000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"提供格式范例\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E6%A0%BC%E5%BC%8F%E8%8C%83%E4%BE%8B\" aria-label=\"提供格式范例 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>提供格式范例</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>对于某些具有特殊格式的输入信息（如年月日等），我们在设计占位符的时候就可以预先把格式写入其中，告诉用户信息输入的必要格式，起到提前防错效果。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"可根据业务场景为输入项提供默认值\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%8F%AF%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE%E4%B8%9A%E5%8A%A1%E5%9C%BA%E6%99%AF%E4%B8%BA%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E9%A1%B9%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E9%BB%98%E8%AE%A4%E5%80%BC\" aria-label=\"可根据业务场景为输入项提供默认值 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>可根据业务场景为输入项提供默认值</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>对于用户而言，有的时候不得不填写一些比较长的表单，而表单中的条目越多，对于用户而言相应耗费的时长、难度越高。符合业务场景的默认值设计，能够有效的缓解用户填写较长表单的时候的麻烦。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"输入建议\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE\" aria-label=\"输入建议 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>输入建议</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>如果需要给用户提供输入建议，请参考<a href=\"\">自动填充</a> <code class=\"language-text\">AutoComplete</code> </li>\n</ul>\n<!--\n\n## 主题\n\n| 内容 | 值           | 默认值  |\n| :--- | :----------- | :------ |\n| icon | icon/nothing | nothing |\n| icon | icon/nothing | nothing |\n-->\n<h2 id=\"相关文档\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3\" aria-label=\"相关文档 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>相关文档</h2>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"/u-design/component/AutoComplete/\">AutoComplete 自动填充</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/u-design/component/Form/\">Form 表单</a></li>\n</ol>","headings":[{"value":"简介","depth":2},{"value":"基本构成","depth":2},{"value":"基本样式","depth":2},{"value":"基础样式","depth":3},{"value":"自定义样式","depth":3},{"value":"尺寸","depth":3},{"value":"基本状态","depth":2},{"value":"设计说明","depth":2},{"value":"避免使用占位符作为标题","depth":3},{"value":"提供格式范例","depth":3},{"value":"可根据业务场景为输入项提供默认值","depth":3},{"value":"输入建议","depth":3},{"value":"相关文档","depth":2}],"fields":{"slug":"/component/list/Input/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"","description":"通过鼠标或键盘输入内容,提供录入信息的能力。","order":null}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/component/list/Button/"},"frontmatter":{"title":""}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/component/list/Form/"},"frontmatter":{"title":""}}},"pageContext":{"id":"a33b9771-4bbb-5bec-ac69-18b7223dd3ef","previousPostId":"d436a57c-4da7-5756-a403-c5a076660050","nextPostId":"e408476f-2c52-5c